  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>This Is A Short Game!!</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About:</h2>King Toad ate another frog...<br><br>After eating a gun, even a small frog like yourself might be able to take him down though. Gun Frog is a unique movement shooter filled with fun characters and thrilling combat. Bounce on lily pads and shoot flies as you explore a vibrant world on an epic journey to defeat King Toad.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173130/extras/896771ae2c554385ba6d1a3322f30077.poster.avif?t=1765989240\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173130/extras/896771ae2c554385ba6d1a3322f30077.webm?t=1765989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast paced physics based movement and combat.<br></li><li> 7 unique bosses and locations<br></li><li> A wide range of silly characters<br></li><li> Lots of frogs</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173130/extras/e308a541a9a0267ea6298b289d9f9a00.poster.avif?t=1765989240\" width=609 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173130/extras/e308a541a9a0267ea6298b289d9f9a00.webm?t=1765989240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
